Name:		perl-Types-Serialiser
Summary:	Simple data types for common serialization formats
Version:	1.01
Release:	13%{?dist}
License:	GPL-1.0-or-later OR Artistic-1.0-Perl
URL:		https://metacpan.org/release/Types-Serialiser
